org.modelio.metamodel.uml.statik

Interface Parameter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<MObject>, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, MObject, ModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BehaviorParameter

    public interface Parameter
extends ModelElement
    Parameter v0.0.9054 The main characteristics of a Parameter are its name, passing mode and type. The return value of an Operation is a specific case managed by a specific Association between Operation and Parameter. In Modelio, a Parameter belongs to its Operation.
